### Register a merchant
POST https://localhost:5001/merchants/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "merchant@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!"
}

### Exchange token
POST https://localhost:5001/merchants/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "merchant@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!"
}

### List templates
GET https://localhost:5001/templates

### Create a store (requires Authorization header)
POST https://localhost:5001/stores
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Downtown Boutique",
  "slug": "downtown-boutique",
  "templateId": "08f8a83b-f0a9-4b80-8bbe-1ecb1c3f4f11"
}

### List store categories (requires Authorization header)
GET https://localhost:5001/stores/{storeId}/categories
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### List marketplace stores
GET https://localhost:5001/marketplace/stores
